    2682 [label="SPDXLicense:\nThis license is essentially a rebranded version of MPL-1.1, but with some\nimportant changes. A new AMENDMENTS section is introduced, which includes an\nadvertisement clause, non-endorsement and no-trademark clauses, as well as\nproduct/project naming rules. These changes are summarised in the new §6.4 where\nit is also explicitly stated that the license is a modificaton on MPL-1.1."
